{"tid":2452011,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"pico 同IPL 想去斑邊隻好啲","createTime":"2021-03-18T13:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:41:12.000Z","uid":114612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"197449679f1d561078082f3ab9ef7fd03cf286bd","tid":2452011,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"見而家好多美容院都係狂sell pico<br />\n但係早兩日去一間所謂醫學美容中心度打<br />\n就話係用Lumenis M22做既<br />\n如果想祛斑 同暗黃應該揀邊隻<br />\n有冇巴打或者絲打可以解答我<br />\n因為呢啲treatments都好貴<br />\n窮J冇錢兩隻都做晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e8339d8d24cd0436f5c52edb0e345be8cf323f","tid":2452011,"uid":328904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"聽過人講pico係打色素，不過通常都係打紋身個啲，M22好似打班係好啲，仲有隻laser唔記得叫咩名係主打斑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61ded42ef0e9c722b9525a1cc8c90103430e86a","tid":2452011,"uid":328904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過人講pico係打色素，不過通常都係打紋身個啲，M22好似打斑係好啲，仲有隻laser唔記得叫咩名係主打斑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e6ea4b4076f35a2ac282c9b2d8bc5680c0502291","tid":2452011,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"Pico for sure"},{"pid":"ffb2c39d28cbfced269ded93334195fe359bf74c","tid":2452011,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d61ded42ef0e9c722b9525a1cc8c90103430e86a","tid":2452011,"uid":328904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過人講pico係打色素，不過通常都係打紋身個啲，M22好似打斑係好啲，仲有隻laser唔記得叫咩名係主打斑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"Oneness<br />\n起唔到佢底<br />\n唔知係冇乜人去定係點<br />\n佢sell我萬七蚊打六次，又唔知市價<br />\n我心大心細緊"},{"pid":"bdc782901d145e25885991ba7e6a51